Class RedBlackTree<String extends java.lang.Comparable<String>,States>

  • java.lang.Object
    • RedBlackTree<String,States>

  • public class RedBlackTree<String extends java.lang.Comparable<String>,States>
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a RedBlackBST datastructure that has strings as its key and the ADT States as its values Only functions that were necessary for our use were brought over from the algorithms textbook code and they were modified for our needs.
    Version:
    3.0 Citation: This code is based off of the RedBlackBST found in the Algorithms textbook and is referencing https://algs4.cs.princeton.edu/code/edu/princeton/cs/algs4/RedBlackBST.java.html
    Author:
    Michael Barreiros, Ben Li
